These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, tiparillo, dunhill
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, orange, lilac
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, scientific
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, blues, ambient
1. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person who likes ivory and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
3. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person who likes ivory is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Cigar          | davidoff      | tiparillo        | dunhill     |
| Color         | lilac | orange | ivory    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | musical       | scientific |
| Music-Genre         | jazz  | blues      | ambient    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, coach, photographer
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, sprite
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, zinnia, bellflower
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, turkish, german
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the italian##1
2. the person drinking juice is the coach##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
4. the coach is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the photographer##3
6. the photographer is in an even position##4
7. the german is between the person drinking juice and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Job           | coach    | photographer | accountant |
| Beverage   | juice | coffee       | sprite   |
| Flower           | bellflower  | zinnia   | rose     |
| Nationality         | turkish | german       | italian   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daffodil, sunflower
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, almond-milk
3 different pets are kept: bird, pony, turtle
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, chef, manager
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the engineer##1
2. the person who growssunflower is the manager##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the person who growsdahlia is between the person drinking tea and the manager##2
5. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the turtle is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Flower          | sunflower | dahlia | daffodil |
| Beverage   | almond-milk     | juice | tea |
| Pet           | pony       | bird   | turtle    |
| Job     | manager      | engineer   | chef |

