.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
House: gothic-revival, tower, wooden
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, dahlia, azalea
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, mystery
There 3 different types of food: banana, peas, cucumber
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the wooden house##1
3. the person who growsazalea is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person eating peas is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
6. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
7. the wooden house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| House         | tower  | gothic-revival       | wooden |
| Flower           | azalea     | dahlia      | daisy   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | mystery     |
| Food   | banana      | cucumber   | peas     |

