.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, water
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, montecristo, aristoff
3 different pets are kept: snake, fish, rat
House: gothic-revival, townhouse, palace
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
6. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the palace house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Beverage      | water     | juice   | coffee         |
| Cigar           | dannemann | montecristo | aristoff |
| Pet   | rat      | fish   | snake            |
| House   | townhouse   | palace  | gothic-revival         |

