.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, monopoly
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, pony
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, december
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, italian, mexican
1. the person who's birthday is in june is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person playing snooker##2
2. the dutch is the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is the italian##1
4. the italian is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
5. the dutch is in an even position##4
6. the dutch is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Game          | monopoly    | mah-jongg     | snooker |
| Pet           | hedgehog | pony | dog      |
| Birthday   | december      | june       | march    |
| Nationality   | italian      | dutch         | mexican     |

