.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-7::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, card-games, woodworking
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda, lemonade
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, go
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, taxi
1. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person driving the roller and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
7. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Hobby          | card-games | camping | woodworking |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | fanta    | lemonade |
| Game   | monopoly  | mah-jongg   | go    |
| Transport     | taxi   | car       | roller |

