.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
House: cape-cod, farmhouse, futuristic
City: hannover, nizza, venice
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, animation, superhero
1. the person traveling to venice is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
5. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
7. the cape-cod house is between the person traveling to nizza and the person watching superhero movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | coffee    | soy-milk  |
| House         | futuristic        | cape-cod   | farmhouse   |
| City   | venice       | hannover    | nizza |
| Movie-Genre     | superhero          | animation | comedy       |

