4. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the librarian is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
7. the freelancer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
