3. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the thai##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the colonial house is in an odd position##4
7. the colonial house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
