2. the owner of the pony is the brazilian##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is in an odd position##4
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
7. the owner of the bird is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
