.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
House: futuristic, art-deco, gothic-revival
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, horror
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, ship, helicopter
City: prague, edinburgh, venice
1. the person traveling to venice is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
7. the art-deco house is between the futuristic house and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| House      | gothic-revival       | art-deco   | futuristic |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror     | disaster |
| Transport           | car      | ship | helicopter    |
| City         | edinburgh  | venice     | prague |

