.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, lemonade
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, indian, polish
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, martial-arts
3 different games are played: chess, backgammon, poker
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
4. the polish is on the far right##1
5. the person watching animation movies is the person playing poker##1
6. the indian is in the middle##1
7. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person playing poker##1
9. the indian is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage           | mirinda | hot-chocolate   | lemonade |
| Nationality   | argentine  | indian    | polish    |
| Movie-Genre         | comedy    | animation | martial-arts   |
| Game     | backgammon  | poker     | chess  |

