.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-14::.
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, ferret, frog
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, scooter, ship
There are 3 different nationalities: american, argentine, turkish
3 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, billiard
1. the american is the owner of the frog##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing snooker is between the person driving the ship and the owner of the hedgehog##2
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
6. the argentine is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Pet         | frog    | ferret   | hedgehog      |
| Transport           | ship | subway    | scooter |
| Nationality   | american       | argentine | turkish      |
| Game         | billiard         | snooker   | backgammon     |

