.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-16::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, peas, tomato
3 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, chess
3 different pets are kept: goat, ferret, chinchilla
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, tennis, parkour
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
7. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Food          | peas     | pear   | tomato     |
| Game   | chess   | backgammon   | monopoly      |
| Pet   | ferret | goat | chinchilla    |
| Sport     | parkour  | swimming   | tennis |

