3. the colombian is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Sport          | volleyball     | ice-hockey | surfing   |
| Cigar         | vegafina   | dannemann | cain |
| Nationality   | pakistani | dutch       | colombian   |
| Pet     | hedgehog     | rabbit  | ferret        |

