.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-19::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, scientific, drama
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, ship, boat
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, may, december
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, rugby
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is the person watching drama movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person watching scientific movies is the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre          | scientific  | epic   | drama |
| Transport   | ship      | boat      | motorbike   |
| Birthday   | june     | december | may |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | cricket   | rugby   |

