.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, azure, blood-red
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, mirinda
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, dunhill, alhambra
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
6. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Color           | chestnut  | blood-red | azure   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | mirinda           | fanta      |
| Cigar           | alhambra   | dunhill          | cain |
| Transport     | boat    | tram           | snowmobile |

 